description: The second group of guys arrived on day five bringing with them Robbie, Atticus, Brendan, Blake and Porter. This is the first time we’ve seen this many SeanCody guys together ever in one film and it ended up being a ton of fun. After some goofing around in the park, everyone headed back to the house to get started. Watching all these guys go at it and do whatever they wanted was something really special. We really let them just pick and choose their own adventure.
title: Winter Getaway: Day 5
